WEBVTT

00:00.168 --> 00:01.781
Previously on "The Whispers"...

00:01.806 --> 00:04.779
Sean was not a perfect husband.
I was not a perfect wife.

00:04.804 --> 00:06.047
Do you love him?

00:06.616 --> 00:07.710
No.

00:07.742 --> 00:09.577
But you had to think about it.

00:09.636 --> 00:11.844
We found Sean's plane
thousands of miles away

00:11.878 --> 00:13.039
from where it was supposed
to have disappeared.

00:13.064 --> 00:14.836
- Peter: What is that thing?
- Wes: Fulgurite.

00:14.861 --> 00:16.664
Drill says he can help
you get what you want

00:16.689 --> 00:18.016
if you help him get what he wants.

00:18.041 --> 00:19.680
Don't you want to know where your dad is?

00:19.705 --> 00:21.836
He's experiencing some kind of memory loss.

00:21.861 --> 00:23.805
Each of your tattoos,
they represent a place?

00:23.830 --> 00:25.055
I don't know until I get there.

00:25.080 --> 00:26.625
- What happens when you do?
- Nothing good.

00:26.650 --> 00:28.938
Sean is trying to cause a meltdown?

00:28.963 --> 00:30.031
Flood the reactor.

00:30.064 --> 00:33.008
Oh, my God, Henry. Henry? Henry?!

00:33.033 --> 00:34.334
Henry: Daddy!

00:34.359 --> 00:35.858
[Rumbling]

00:36.577 --> 00:38.414
[Grunts]

00:39.406 --> 00:41.656
Can someone tell me
what the hell I just saw?

00:41.681 --> 00:43.586
Three people just walked
out of that facility.

00:43.611 --> 00:44.922
They're clean. Whole area is.

00:44.947 --> 00:45.836
Can you hear me?

00:45.861 --> 00:47.397
It was supposed to be a secret

00:47.422 --> 00:49.855
between me and... Drill.

